<emphasis id="E4F7EAF3FFB8FFB134F0F99B9646971E" box="[151,378,1594,1615]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="351">Chvalaea catarinensis</emphasis>
Ale Rocha, 2006
</taxonomicName>
, strong apical setae highlighted. Scale bars: Figs 7–8 = 0.5 mm; Figs 13–14 = 0.2 mm.
